author: tensorflower-gardener
message:
Use `ifrt::LoadedExecutable::GetHumanReadableProgramText()` to implement `Executable.as_text()`.

`Executable.as_text()` currently relies on `Executable` returning HLO modules. Since with certain IFRT backends, `Executable`s may not have HLO modules, `as_text()` would previously return empty strings in such situations.
